We determined the ordering of the pair of fish relative to the direction of motion of the group centre using the following calculations and linear transformations. For each video frame we identified the mean coordinates of the pair of fish $(\bar{x}(t),\bar{y}(t))$ (that is, the group centre). We then estimated the velocity of the group centre at time $t$ using:

